{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"茜子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-15","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJ58zzeAvjk9egsh7pI0xaJnzicWDeplo17IiaNXickic8DF3Zlst8Q0iapLbQtCHZvpOerIF8aXibO6obBD9TuUW7KAq/0","content":"第三类客户：因为他们刚消费完，更容易对促销有反应，并一定程度上提高他们的低消费频率和金额","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7774,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492271521000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"郭丽敏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-15","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay3J1MHPAxQGN6yrKdJbWI9X6xzmUKCPn78X0urjAKAQWicAAibcgQvrz2ribr8qfnCMNsbkBMjhIw9b/0","content":"推送给1","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7747,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492250490000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"王佳","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-15","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AywoaJCYTv4hicL3wib7fApyhLPNJiaroIhefibZ5St8K9AWkmRhDQ3astuE22Q5cDMLXKe5anwROuryia/0","content":"<p>流量包套餐一般以月，也就是30天计算，因此假设其统计周期为30天，取月中15日为统计日期，则R在15-30为高，14以下为低。由于题目未指明RFM是针对新套餐做的限定条件，还是针对某一类（比如与新套餐类似）套餐的限定条件，因此我选择其RFM值是与新套餐类似的购买行为限定条件。</p><p>用户类型1:RFM值都高，说明这类用户是价值高的用户，消费意愿和能力强，降低R值难度较大，营销方向应该是巩固关系，不是新套餐的目标用户。</p><p>用户类型2:R值很低，也就是说，消费间隔时间短，说明这是潜在用户，需要提高F值和M值，有效的方法，一是提高其现在使用套餐的门槛（我觉得自己够奸商的），提供其新套餐选择；二是针对新套餐上市，进行短信促销和限时打折。</p><p>用户类型3:<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\">R高，F低，M低，我比较难理解这类用户，也许是农村的老人，不愿意多花钱的，因此不是新套餐的潜在用户。</span></p><p>用户类型4:<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\">R低，F低，M高。M高说明对价格不敏感，也导致了R和F相对低的原因，因为钱放里边了（比如一年），这种类型的客户，就不要去打扰他了，生日或节日的时候，给他祝福并顺便推销新套餐就好。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7740,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492246673000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"浅紫","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-12","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay5Qias5Y6BOJq0bibrmkolNJFtbyicK1y9rN41JY4SIw04awshr8lhByygakZc9SVzOfPej1XNTbShq/0","content":"待补充","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7572,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491967119000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"FVian.","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-11","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEj5WVrH3IVqXh9Mcec8y3PDialWkVgibeHwjmiaS4FL83t6iaYiaWWBuSC7T5cS6MSndAH1ibYroW492FK/0","content":"<p>推荐给第一类客户。</p><p>因为这类客户首先已经长期未使用服务，但从以往迹象来看使用频次高，并且消费金额高，也许正是因为对于流量的需求高所产生的费用高导致他近期减少使用频次。可以通过推出包月套餐，继续吸引此类客户，恢复以往使用习惯。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7547,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491920411000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"盛夏tl","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQLZSOLpBibDcibZ6sFXGjaugXibNJwMAvZF35uJNo0TzNd8uGdLrfymhDiav0qNFFCZzEIQIxyrWNEPw/0","content":"3 4","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7482,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491832851000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Bryce","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-09","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoEUMhO4vLWCnI4Q4mvkDusPBDh3XsxUEuQ6Ticu4ZR084FGF6lOUrUZsWMgnKK1squCngsib37KZEib/0","content":"如果是一次性的，推荐1<div>如果是持续性的，推荐4</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7421,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491720660000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"影子（one life one liver）","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-08","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay7P6qrmu6EFgMxv9yByicqqSVMrdaJoMs4TEyich23rD3ictMbhBfngbwia0x0G3qzXEM5ib5SQ8bx5vQ/0","content":"包月流量属于高频低价值商品，适应RFM，推荐给购1类客户。R应该用长短来表示，说明最近购买流量，F高说明购买频率高，M高，优质客户。本质上还是二八原则。其次是4类客户。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7401,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491639561000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"潇洒鳕鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-07","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98UyLlHC2Q1gMdxzMwDhQicAb4RP8PgibVuS6OEZoCGk0aIWo8mMahY8wu6ic8YFFqdsInJgJAaxbe58CIgsSXQC94U/0","content":"<div>我应该会首先选择第一类客户，其次是第四类客户。原因如下：</div><div>第一类客户的消费金额高，对于包月套餐这样能够省钱的方法会很积极。另外他们的消费频率高，说明他们在使用中非常活跃。这类客户是较为优质的客户。</div><div>第四类客户虽然消费频率低，但是他们的消费间隔低且金额高，这类客户值得关注，因此采用包月这种可以省钱的套餐，能够留住这类客户。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7308,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491526068000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"咕咕","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-06","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoAOwic4GNKoz5oR3ECE0v0lAicujK9wBbRPMVWrjBNRath8ZicUnKVKP1TicLlXAlKrf2HJNO0Vv5SH5/0","content":"最应该推荐给第四类：高消费价值客户，且消费间隔小，刚消费不久，对于宣传推介反应概率最大，可以想办法提高其消费频率；<div>还可以推荐给第一类：消费价值高且频繁，但间隔较久，可以想法促成再次购买。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7301,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491484675000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Leo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-05","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSic0ds8BMCibGZ2OUAZx2wvLS7l0JfCujUnFH561QnYtbqvZs2sAcicsmYHVHeJSgYia20o2R8WfC0mn/0","content":"<p>题目有点歧义，2G包月流量包，是2G网络的包月流量还是包一个月总共2个G的流量？……</p><p>首先无论哪一个，优先选择必定是第一类客户了，最好的客户。</p><p>其次，如果是前者，第四类比较适合，因为这类客户是提高注意重点维护的高价值顾客，购买高价格持久型服务的可能性高。</p><p>最后，如果是后者，第三类比较合适，因为这类客户是需要挖掘购买能力的潜在顾客，购买新产品可能性高。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7019,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491395452000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"月时纪","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-05","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEIbzFiaBIfgyNUKic44GBr1eWTAlOTx5XY6ysPmSVN3T5VyAxcm9kysawGgIenuyEd6NUrHVmGhiarpA/0","content":"<div>建议R用长短来描述，不用高低，我实在不能理解高是指间隔时间长，还是间隔时间短……</div><div>鉴于2G的流量不少，但是还要看客户是怎么使用的，需要分析客户此前购买的套餐的使用方式，有的人可能一周就用完了，有的人可能两个月都用不完。</div><div>最好的客户应该是R短，F高，M高的客户，这样的客户把流量当WIFI用啊；</div><div>其次可以推给R短，F高，M低的客户，因为经常性买少的流量包，看到优惠的多的流量包会觉得更划算；</div><div>再次还有R长，F低，M高的客户，这样的客户可能会嫌多频次购买麻烦，一次性购买较多的流量，可以用较长一段时间。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7219,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491359474000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"郭舒简","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XRibESzncllLeNVVgOoXl3jmKXQT07IR1fYwPRIgiboTXU2tjiaAn3zpZ6cp8iaIvcTMxyrcwRR0P62w/0","content":"中国移动的流量包：<div><br></div><div>- 低：5元30M，10元70M</div><div>- 中：20元150M，30元500M</div><div>- 高：50元1G，70元2G</div><div><br></div><div>我会先分析用户过去6个月的数据流量使用情况。一般来说，如果客户购买了流量包月会每个月消费一次（现在按零头买流量的很少了）。这里的R高我理解为长时间未购买。所以R最大值应为31天。</div><div>低：0-10天</div><div>中：11-20天</div><div>高：21-31天</div><div>F高说明他经常买加油包，可以向他推销2G套餐（如果原来就用的是3G就算了）。</div><div><br></div><div>1. 消费间隔时间长，经常购买加油包，消费金额高，首先推荐给他们。</div><div>2. 近期有购买行为，数据流量使用较少，是需要挖掘购买潜力的客户。</div><div>3. 被遗弃的客户，不用考虑</div><div>4. 近期有购买行为，频率低金额高，是需要维护的客户。</div><div><br></div><div>优先级：1-4-2</div><div><br></div>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":1,"submitId":7205,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491316087000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Grace谷","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-03","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaELv640C7eLVwPdYLyP2jMRQblcFyjjnsPKxUneMS95dD1tQ8s3Dfh0c7THxBxcan2Jcg0o92SVV3w/0","content":"第3类","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7140,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491219365000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Keep moving","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-03","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEqF6jufbDorn80rkbIhg1pDXpV90htcEkxHRGhTY88saZrWAFhcBVEQv1wBv3X8aHIsLOedWCxHj/0","content":"<p>我会推荐给3.4类型的客户。因为这类客户更有潜在购买力。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">③R高，F低，M低 这类客户购买时间间隔短，对我们产品产品有较深印象。应马上给他们推荐包月套餐，即使不能推荐成功，也能强化该套餐在其心中的印象。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">④R低，F低，M高 &nbsp;这类客户购买周期和频度低，是习惯一次性购买的用户。应研究其购买规律，在TA下一次支付月租费之前（通常为月底），给TA推送新套餐信息，让TA加大即时购买的可能。</span><br></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">不推荐给1.2类客户，因为他们没有购买潜力。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">①R高，F高，M高这类客户是我们最好最忠实的客户。所有得分到达最高值，同时意味着他们基本没有潜在购买力可以挖掘了。这时我们要做的就是维护他们的购买力及忠诚度。可通过积分换购礼品服务，VIP特权等行为来维护。</span><br></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">②R低，F低，M低 从数据来看，这类客户对我们品牌认可度较低，不建议把营销资源投入到这部分客户上。</span><br></span></span></span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7128,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491198765000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"灿灿","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-02","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJrWntUHNk0zHK1D4Erd9HKhAcDtR33woSI7GNbwLt73SrysUaw3L8spMJicd8quTia0pEUpia9JDtkGJVNX9lAkp5/0","content":"<p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">优先选择</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">1<span style=\"margin: 0px;\">，次选择</span>4<span style=\"margin: 0px;\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">流量消费频率从高到低。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">流量消费频率从高到低。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">流量消费金额从从高到底。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">我们就可以把顾客分成类，对其进行数据分析，然后制定我们的营销策略。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">对于那些最近期的消费用户，频率较高且金额较大的，一定是高端的优质用户，区分出用户后，排好优先级进行营销。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6949,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491110111000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Skylar","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEm0gAl9eEUcROZ9BLhECn24VjQKCGzIZyXViaagNS0GiaibO33zLQZkqBdOLpgLeh3wWoEJ4dyYiaPl7/0","content":"产品：2G包月流量包套餐(属于高端产品)\n①R高，F高，M高\n推荐；周期长、频率高、消费金额高，属于高端消费群，黏性强的客户\n②R低，F低，M低\n不推荐；适合低层级套餐，否则会造成浪费\n③R高，F低，M低\n不推荐；适合最低层级套餐\n④R低，F低，M高\n推荐；周期短，频率低，但是消费高，可以根据实际情况包月","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6908,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490924844000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"lanlan","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-28","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoABxary8VgXcewR1AmF19vgqh1yjicvfMjehwnN9BCtpicJfHXYmt3tEsP23v1u2lfVGIFicncrooia2/0","content":"    我是中国移动的产品经理，最近我们公司推出了2G包月流量包套餐，该套餐适用于每个月流量使用量较大的用户群体。为了实现精准营销，我们对客户的流量使用情况进行了分析，最终确定主要将该套餐推荐给其中的第一类和第四类用户。\n\n    我们利用RFM模型（R：消费间隔时间、F：消费频率、M：消费金额）将客户分为了四类。\n\n    第一类用户消费间隔时间距离统计时间较长，他们的消费频率较高，消费金额也很高，这类用户对品牌忠诚度很高，但最近有一段时间没有消费，有流失的可能，因此需要主动保持联系。而且包月套餐对这类消费金额较高的客户比较有吸引力，应该向他们推荐公司的新套餐。\n\n    第二类用户消费间隔时间距离统计时间较短，他们的消费频率较低，消费金额低。虽然他们最近消费过，但由于消费金额低，对于大流量的包月套餐可能没有这方面需求，因此可以不予考虑。\n\n    第三类用户消费间隔时间距离统计时间较长，他们的消费频率较低，消费金额低。这类客户品牌忠诚度不高，在资源有限的情况下，可暂时不予考虑新套餐的推荐。\n\n    第四类用户消费间隔时间距离统计时间较短，他们的消费频率较低，但消费金额高。他们的品牌忠诚度虽然有限，但仍属于有潜力的客户，而且最近刚刚消费过，应该向他们推荐新套餐，以长期维护这部分客户。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5605,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490684537000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"kerry","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-25","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay5cUlGv2ibxydlESCOjsMG6yNquicDV2grtRHY4e6BREibMTu7aYqiaYHGMSVmVfneOdxIhRkLicP5at1/0","content":"3","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5670,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490445670000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"施伟","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-23","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEo9P2jC2S2gtzmiaPWycP2Fd6c8Lvunc8sP0iapaIrzxCur3tMr7Bia6kYfGXE4Pn3CLxmAUW8nr6ZK/0","content":"我会选择3.4号，给他们推荐的，3号间隔时间小，提高他频率和消费金额。4号消费高，提高他频率，时间间隔小。来提高我们的销售。1号各项指标很高，就不用推荐了，维护好就行。2号是放弃客户。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5159,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490236619000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":false},"code":200}
